19
00:01:01,760 --> 00:01:07,480
And anybody who computes, who's living in the real world,

20
00:01:07,480 --> 00:01:10,040
is using linear algebra.

21
00:01:10,040 --> 00:01:13,120
You're taking a differential equation,

22
00:01:13,120 --> 00:01:16,320
you're taking your model, making it discrete,

23
